## Network Traffic Monitoring & Attack Detection

Development of a system for packet capture, traffic analysis, and attack detection in O-RAN environments.

### 🔍 Focus Areas
- Network traffic analysis
- Intrusion detection
- Attack simulation in RAN environments

### 🛠 Tools
- Wireshark
- Python-based analysis tools
- Linux networking stack

### 📌 Impact
Supports security evaluation of virtualized network infrastructures.

